QuestData.Title: Mo'mor Might Know
QuestData.Description: We know the Warsong packleader that attacked the caravan is in Telaar. She has the blueprints.$B$BWe don't know where she is down there, but there's one who might.$B$BVindicator Mo'mor was last seen alive, but taken prisoner. If he's still alive, he might know where the blueprints are.
QuestData.RewardText: Please forgive me. I'm in no condition to stand, commander.
